{"tid":944528,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"重慶礦難釀7死3傷　同集團煤礦兩月內第二宗","createTime":"2018-12-17T08:17:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-17T08:17:42.000Z","uid":75969,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"161e63f8d11ddb503d5d8dc2ef7dd6e379f148b3","tid":944528,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T08:17:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20181217/s00004/4e891dcdac4318675a00d6157a750d3f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20181217%2Fs00004%2F4e891dcdac4318675a00d6157a750d3f.jpg&h=d10ccee1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">圖1之1 - 中國頻頻發生礦難事故，採礦業死亡人數為全世界最高。(資料圖片)</span><br />\n<br />\n重慶逢春煤礦發生奪命意外，一輛煤礦料車的連接裝置斷裂，令料車直衝煤礦，造成7人死亡和3人受傷，意外原因有待調查。<br />\n<br />\n事發的煤礦屬重慶市能源投資集團，集團另一位於重慶的煤礦兩個月前發生氣體爆炸，造成5死4傷。內地礦難事故頻生，採礦業死亡人數為全世界最高，包括今年10月，山東一處煤礦倒塌，造成21名煤礦工人死亡，僅1人獲救。<br />\n<br />\n中國人命是最不值錢的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/兩岸/article/20181217/s00004/1545031517031/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E5%85%A9%E5%B2%B8%2Farticle%2F20181217%2Fs00004%2F1545031517031%2F&d=bVhSs0u1UTjocNzuugnzMAEk2Noh57F05xbgvjQdsX8%3D&h=e66f303c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E5%85%A9%E5%B2%B8%2Farticle%2F20181217%2Fs00004%2F1545031517031%2F&h=24144733\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/兩岸/article/20181217/s00004/1545031517031/</a>"}]}